Package com.escape.games.resource

Interface Summary
GLResource Marker interface for GL resources.
 

Class Summary
Framebuffer Support for GL Framebuffer Uses 16-bit depth attachment and RGBA color attachment.
IndexBufferObject Implementation of GL Index Buffer Object resource.
Shader Implementation for GL 2.x shader program.
ShaderBuilder Fluent builder for creating custom shaders.
Texture Base implementation for OpenGL 2D texture from application resource.
VertexBufferObject Implementation of GL Vertex Buffer Object resource.
